The Supplier shall supply industrial overhead sectional doors:

Model: {{doorModel}}
Quantity: {{doorQty}}

Per door:
- Opening: {{openW}} × {{openH}} mm
- Panel: {{panelType}}, min {{panelThk}} mm, {{panelProf}}
- Ext colour: {{extCol}}
- Int colour: {{intCol}}
- Rail: {{rail}}
- Operation: {{op}}
- Power: {{power}}
- Wicket door: {{wicket}}
- Glazing: {{glazing}}

Safety (mandatory): light barrier, pinch protection, emergency release, safety edge.

The Supplier shall confirm in the quotation: type, U-value (panel and complete door), wind/water/air class, cycle rating, speed, DoP/CE, weight, headroom/sideroom requirements.

STM reserves the right to reject non-compliant alternatives.

The Supplier shall supply per door:
- Control: {{ctrlType}}
- Remote: {{remote}}
- Traffic lights: {{traffic}}
- Cable to {{cable}} point
- Emergency stop

The Supplier shall state any required accessories not included in the above scope.
